iginal Norwegian Folktales of Asbjornsen & Moe |location=Minneapolis |publisher=University of Minnesota Press |year=2019 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4oK9DwAAQBAJ&pg=PT27 |pages= |isbn=1-452-96455-6<!--9781452964553-->}}</ref>\n\n}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:|Askeladden}}\n[[Category:Norwegian fairy tales|Askeladden]]\n[[Category:Scandinavian folklore|Askeladden]]\n[[Category:Trolls|Askeladden]]\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toFolktale(link changed toFolklore genre) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/About_Ash_Lad,_Who_Stole_the_Troll%27s_Silver_Ducks,_Coverlet,_and_Golden_Harp"}
